==現況==
2012年有教友142,112人（佔轄區總人口9.7%）、十三個堂區、七十七名司鐸。教區主教現時[[教座出缺|出缺]]<ref>{{cite press release |title=Resignations and Appointments, 08.07.2019 |url=https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/en/bollettino/pubblico/2019/07/08/190708a.html |publisher=Holy See Press Office |accessdate=2019-08-24 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20190824151512/https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/en/bollettino/pubblico/2019/07/08/190708a.html |archivedate=2019-08-24 |language=en |date=2019-07-08 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

